@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="card">

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <hr />

    <p>
        The Global Logistics Management System (GLMS) is committed to
        protecting the privacy and confidentiality of all logistics,
        financial, and contractual information stored within the system.
    </p>

    <h3>1. Information Collection</h3>

    <p>
        GLMS collects operational business information including:
    </p>

    <ul>
        <li>Client details</li>
        <li>Contract agreements</li>
        <li>Service request records</li>
        <li>Financial transaction data</li>
        <li>Uploaded PDF agreements</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. Data Security</h3>

    <p>
        Uploaded contract documents are securely stored on the server
        and restricted to authorized personnel only.
    </p>

    <p>
        The system validates uploaded files and only permits PDF
        documents to reduce security risks.
    </p>

    <h3>3. Currency API Integration</h3>

    <p>
        GLMS uses third-party currency exchange APIs to retrieve
        real-time exchange rates for international logistics reporting.
    </p>

    <p>
        No sensitive financial account information is shared with
        external providers.
    </p>

    <h3>4. Contract Compliance</h3>

    <p>
        The system automatically validates contract status before
        processing service requests to ensure operational compliance.
    </p>

    <h3>5. User Responsibilities</h3>

    <p>
        Authorized users are responsible for maintaining the
        confidentiality of their login credentials and ensuring
        uploaded documents are accurate and legitimate.
    </p>

    <h3>6. System Monitoring</h3>

    <p>
        Administrative activities and operational transactions may be
        logged for auditing, security monitoring, and compliance
        purposes.
    </p>

    <h3>7. Contact</h3>

    <p>
        For privacy or compliance concerns, please contact:
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>TechMove Logistics</strong><br />
        Email: support@techmove.com
    </p>

</div>